hadiths[47]{hadithnumber,text}:
2090,"Hazrat Rifaa bin Araaba Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab qism khatey to yun farmatey : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai."
2091,"Hazrat Rifaa bin Araaba Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Allah key samney gawahi deta hun ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jo qism khatey they wo yun hoti thi : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai."
2092,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aksar in alfaz key sath qism khatey they : dilon ko pherney waley ki qism ! (baat is tarah) nahin ."
2093,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qism hoti thi : (لا وَأَسْتَغْفِرُاللَّهَ),''nahin ! aur main Allah sey maghfirat aur bakhshish ka Talib hun.''"
2094,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen apney baap ki qism khatey suna to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala tumhen baapon ki qism khaney sey mana farmata hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : phir mainey (kabhi) baap dada ki qism nahin khai , na apni taraf sey , na kisi ki baat naqal kartey huye."
2095,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : buton ki qasmen na khaya karo, aur na baap dada ki qasmen khaao."
2096,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs qism khatey waqt ye keh dey : qism hai ""laat aur uzza ki"" usey chahiye ke (fauran) ""لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ""  keh ley."
2097,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey laat aur uzza ki qism khai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaho : (لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ), ''akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin.'' phir baain taraf teen baar thook do aur (shetan sey) Allah ki panah maango aur dobara ye ghalati na karna."
2098,"Hazrat Sabit bin Zuhaak (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Islam key ilawa doosrey mazhab (mein chaley janey) ki jaan boojh kar jhooti qism khai to wo wesey hi hai jaisey usney kaha."
2099,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney suna ke eik aadmi keh raha tha : (agar yun huwa to) yaqinan main us waqt Yahudi hun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (yahudiyat ya dozakh) wajib ho gaee."
2100,"Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kahey : (agar falan baat yun hui to) mera Islam sey koi talluq nahin, isliye agar usney jhoot kaha to wo wesey hi ho gaya jaisey usney kaha tha (kafir ho gaya). aur agar sachcha huwa to bhi usey pura Islam nasib nahin hoga."
2101,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko apney baap ki qism khatey suna to farmaya : apney baapon ki qasmen na khaya karo . aur jo shakhs Allah ki qism khaye usey chahiye ke sach boley. aur jis key liye (uskey mutalbey par) Allah ki qism khai jaey, usey chahiye ke (is qism par) razi ho jaey. aur jo Allah sey razi nahin hota, uska Allah sey koi talluq nahin."
2102,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hazrat Esa ibn Maryam (Alaihissalam) ney eik shakhs ko chori kartey dekha to farmaya : kya tu ney chori ki hai? usney kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! (mainey chori) nahin (ki). Hazrat Esa (Alaihissalam) ney farmaya : main Allah par eman lata hun, aur apni aankh ko jhooti kehta hun."
2103,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism todnai padti hai ya is par sharminda hona padta hai."
2104,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney qism khai aur  ""إِنْ شَاءَاللہ""  kaha to us ko is shart ka faeyda hoga ."
2105,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney qism khai aur Inshallah kaha to chahey wo (apney iradey sey) ruju kar ley, chahey (irada qaaim) rehney dey (aur wo kaam kar ley jiski qism khai hai) wo qism todney wala (shumar) nahin hoga."
2106,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney qism khai aur Inshallah kaha, uski qism nahin tooteygi."
2107,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main qabila banu Ash'ar key chand afrad key sath sawariyan talab karney key liye Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main tumhen sawariyan mohaiyya nahin karunga. aur merey paas sawari key janwer nahin hain. Hazrat Abu-Musa ney kaha : hum log, jab tak Allah ney chaha, (Madina mein) thehrey, phir aap key paas kuchh oont aagaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen safed kohaanon wali (moti tazi) teen oontniyaan dilwa den.  jab hum rawana huye to hamney eik doosrey sey kaha : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein sawariyan talab karney key liye hazir huye they to aap ney qism kha li thi ke hamein sawariyan mohaiyya nahin karaengey, phir hamein sawariyan mohaiyya farma den. chalo wapis chalen (aur daryaft karen ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen bhool kar sawariyan mohaiyya na farma di hon). chunanche hum khidmat mein hazir huye aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum aap ki khidmat mein sawariyan talab karney aaye they to aap ney qism kha li thi ke aap hamen sawariyan mohaiyya nahin farmaeyngey, phir aap ney hamein sawariyan mohaiyya farma den. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mainey tumhen sawariyan nahin den balke Allah ney tumhen sawariyan di hain. qism hai Allah ki ! main to inshallah jo bhi qism khaaunga, phir mujhey dusri surat (qasam puri karney sey) behtar malum hogi to main apni qism ka kaffara dey dunga aur behtar kaam kar lunga. ya farmaya : main behtar kaam kar lunga aur apni qism ka kaffara dey dunga."
2108,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs koi qism khaye , phir dusri chiz us sey behtar malum ho to usey chahiye ke behtar kaam kar ley aur apni qism ka kaffara ada kar dey."
2109,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Jushmi (Rahimahullah) ney apney walid (Hazrat Malik bin Nazlaa Jushmi (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat ki, unhoney farmaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey paas mera chacha zaad bhai aata hai (kisi baat par naraz ho kar) main qism kha leta hun ke usey kuchh nahin dunga, na us sey sila rehmi karunga. aap ney farmaya : apni qism ka kaffara ada kar do."
2110,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney qata' rehmi ki qism khai, ya kisi najaaiz kaam ki qism khai to is qism ka pura karna yehi hai ke usey chhod dey."
2111,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib Apney walid sey, wo apney dada sey bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney koi qism khai, phir dusri baat us sey behtar malum hui to us (qasam waley ghalat kaam) ko chhod dey. usey chhodna hi uska kaffara hai."
2112,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kaffaarey key tor par eik saa (khushk) khajuren den aur logon ko bhi yehi hukm diya. jis key paas (khajuren) na hon, wo nisf (aadha) saa gehun dey dey."
2113,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : koi aadmi apney ghar walon ko wusat key sath khana deta tha aur koi tangi key sath deta tha. tab ye aayat nazil hui : (أَوْسَطِ ما تُطْعِمُونَ أَهْلِيكُمْ),''osat darjey ka khana jo tum apney ghar walon ko khilatey ho.''"
2114,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs apni qism par israr karta hai to Allah key yahan wo us kaffaarey sey ziyada gunah ka murtakib (mujrim) hai jis ka usey hukm diya gaya hai. Imam Ibne-Maja ney eik aur sanad sey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hi sey mazkura baala riwayat key hum maana riwayat bayan ki hai."
2115,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein qism deney waley ki qism puri karney ka hukm diya ."
2116,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Safwan ya Hazrat Safwan bin Abdur-Rehman Qarshi (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jis din Makka Fateh huwa , wo apney walid ko ley kar khidmat mein hazir huye aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hijrat mein merey walid ko bhi shareek kar lijiye (unhen muhajrin mein shumar kar lijiye). aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (ab) koi hijrat nahin. wo Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key paas chaley gaey, aur kaha : aap ney mujhey pahchaanaa? Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : haan (tab unhoney apna waqia bayan kiya) to Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sirf qamis pehney huye (un key sath) chal diye, chadar bhi na odhi. aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap falan sahab sey waqif hain aur un sey hamarey jo talluqaat hain (wo bhi aap ko malum hain) wo apney walid ko ley kar hazir huye hain ke aap un sey hijrat ki baiat lein to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (ab) koi hijrat nahin. Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main aap ko qism deta hun. (is par) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney haath badha kar un sahab ka haath chhu liya aur farmaya : mainey apney chacha ki qism puri ki hai aur hijrat koi nahin. ye riwayat Yazeed bin Abi Ziyad ki sanad sey bhi isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2117,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi qism khaye to yun na kahey : jo Allah aur to chahey balke yun kahey : jo Allah chahey, uskey baad jo to chahey."
2118,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik musalman ney khuwab mein dekha ke ehale kitab key eik aadmi (kisi Yahudi ya esai) sey uski mulaqat hui. usney kaha : tum (musalman) achchhey log ho, agar shirk na karo. tum kehtey ho : jo Allah aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chahen. us aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye khuwab sunaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism hai Allah ki ! main bhi tumhari ye baat mehsus kar raha tha. tum yun kaha karo : jo Allah chahey, phir jo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)  chahen.mazkoora baala riwayat eik dusri sanad sey Hazrat Tufail bin Sakhbara sey bhi isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2119,"Hazrat Suwed bin Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey mulaqat key liye rawana huye. hamarey sath Hazrat Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Hazrat Wayl (Raziallahu anhu) ko unkey eik dushman ney pakad liya to logon ney qism khaney mein harj mehsus kiya. mainey qism kha li ke wo merey bhai hain (ye zahir kiya ke ye Wayl bin Hajar nahin). usney unhen chhod diya, phir hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (waqiaa) arz kiya ke doosrey afrad ney qism khaney mein harj mehsus kiya aur mainey qism kha li ke wo merey bhai hain. to aap ney farmaya : tum ney sach kaha. musalman musalman ka bhai hota hai."
2120,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism , qism dilaney waley ki niyat par hoti hai."
2121,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teri qism usi mafhoom par waqey hogi jis par tera sathi (qasam dilaney wala) tujhey sachcha samjhey.
2122,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nazar manney sey mana kiya aur farmaya : iskey zariey sey kanjus (key haath) sey (maal) nikalwaayaa jata hai."
2123,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nazar Adam key betey ko iskey siwa kuchh nahin dila sakti jo uskey liye muqaddar kar diya gaya hai. taqdir nazar par ghalib aa jati hai, jo uski qismat mein hai wo ho jaeyga. lekin nazar key zariey sey bakheel (kanjoos) sey (kuchh na kuchh) niklwa liya jata hai. is tarah is par wo kaam (gharib ki madad karna) aasan ho jata hai jo pehley aasan nahin tha, halanke Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : to kharch kar, main tujh par kharch karunga (tujhey duniya mein bhi dun ga)."
2124,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gunah key kaam ki koi nazar nahin aur jis chiz ka insan Malik nahin, uski koi nazar nahin."
2125,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gunah key kaam ki koi nazar nahin aur uska kaffara qism ka kaffara hai.
2126,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah ki itaat ki nazar maaney, usey chahiye ke Allah ki itaat kerey. aur jo shakhs Allah ki nafarmani ki nazar maaney, usey chahiye ke Allah ki nafarmani na kerey."
2127,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney nazar maana aur uska naam na liya, uska kaffara qism ka kaffara hai."
2128,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney nazar maana aur uska naam na liya (ta'yyun na kiya), uska kaffara qism ka kaffara hai. aur jisney nazar maana jisey wo pura karney ki taqat nahin rakhta, uska kaffara bhi qism ka kaffara hai. aur jisney aisi nazar maana jisey pura karney ki wo taqat rakhta hai, usey chahiye ke nazar puri kerey."
2129,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey jahiliyat main eik nazar maani. Islam qubul karney key baad mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey daryaft kiya to aap ney mujhey nazar puri karney ka hukm diya."
2130,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey bawaana key maqam par oont zibeh karney ki nazar maana hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : terey dil mein jahiliyat wali koi baat to nahin? usney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : apni nazar puri kar ley.
2131,Hazrat Memuna binte Kardam Yasariyya‬ (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unkey walid (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey miley jabke wo (oont par apney walid key) peechhey sawar thin. unhoney kaha : mainey bawaana key maqam par oont zibeh karney ki nazar maana hai to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya wahan koi but hai? unhoney arz kiya : nahin. aap ney farmaya : apni nazar puri kar ley. ye riwayat eik dusri sanad sey bhi Hazrat Memuna binte Kardam (Raziallahu anha) sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai.
2132,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha ke un ki walida key zimmey nazar thi, wo nazar puri kiye baghair faut ho gaeen to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uski taraf sey tum puri karo."
2133,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik khatoon Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : Allah key Rasool ! meri walida faut ho gaee hain aur unkey zimmey nazar key rozey they. wo nazar puri karney sey pehley hi faut ho gaeen. to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uski taraf sey wali rozey rakhey.
2134,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke un ki behan ney nangey paon aur nangey sar pedal safar (kar key Haj) karney ki nazar maan li. unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat batai to aap ney farmaya : usey hukm do ke sawari par bethey, (sar par) dupatta ley aur teen rozey rakh ley."
2135,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik boodhey ko apney do beton key darmiyan (un ka sahara ley kar) chaltey dekha to farmaya : iska kya maamla hai? uskey beton ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! isney nazar maan rakhi hai. aap ney farmaya : badey miyan ! sawar ho jao ! Allah Taala tum sey aur tumhari nazar sey mustaghni (beniyaaz) hai.
2136,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Makka Mukarrama mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka guzar eik shakhs key paas sey huwa jo dhoop mein khada tha to aap ney farmaya : ye kya maamla hai? logon ney arz kiya : usney nazar maana hai ke roza rakhega, raat tak saye mein nahin aayega, kalam nahin kerega aur khada rahega. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey chahiye ke kalam kerey. saye mein aaye, bethey aur apna roza pura kerey. Imam Ibne-Maja ney mazkura riwayat Husain bin Muhammad bin Shana Waasti key wastey sey bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey guzishta hadees ki tarah bayan ki."
